ing: 1 (3.4 ounce) package instant vanilla pudding mix
1 (8 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
des: "Spear your favorite fruit on a toothpick and dip it! It will taste fabulous with this creamy vanilla dip!"
ins: In a medium bowl, mix together the vanilla pudding mix, frozen whipped topping, cream cheese, confectioner's sugar and milk.  Serve chilled.
